Author: 2thesun
Text: 200isplentysweet on Instagram has this DELICIOUS overnight oats with pumpkin purée   https://plentysweet.blog/2019/09/26/wake-up-and-smell-the-pumpkin-overnight-oats/  it’s cold but I’ve tried it heated up and it’s delicious. super filling and yummy and tastes exactly like fall :) she has some other recipes too with pumpkins on her website but i have yet to try them
